        "title": "禁·风灵作成·柒伍同构贰型",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/28de70f699de4ba7cf0f77f2fcfb1483_7275114095131387912.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆发</color>\n造成1点 <color=#99ffff>风元素伤害</color> ，召唤 <color=#ffffff>大型风灵</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "大型风灵",
        "title": "大型风灵",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_9042605472783550235.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>召唤物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>结束阶段：</color> 造成2点 <color=#80ffd7>风元素伤害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数：3</color>\n<color=#ffffff>我方角色或召唤物引发扩散反应后：</color> 转换此牌的元素类型，改为造成被扩散的元素类型的伤害。（离场前仅限一次）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/10/88072335/b91de96bc6f45b8b9a5b10ab4a127a88_1490621129884252374.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "风元素伤害",
        "title": "风元素伤害",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_1328299654435191759.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "和已附着的元素发生元素反应：\n【 <color=#80ffd7>风元素</color> + <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>扩散（冰）</color> ：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰元素伤害\n【 <color=#80ffd7>风元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>扩散（水）</color> ：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水元素伤害\n【 <color=#80ffd7>风元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>扩散（火）</color> ：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火元素伤害\n【 <color=#80ffd7>风元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>扩散（雷）</color> ：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷元素伤害"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "规则术语",
        "title": "规则术语",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2501942162550169625.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ece5d8>可用次数</color>\n此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> 耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
